@baseUrl = http://127.0.0.1:8080
@controlToken = replace-with-BOT_CONTROL_TOKEN

### Evaluate strategy and submit a Bybit testnet/live order
POST {{baseUrl}}/execution/evaluate-and-submit
Authorization: Bearer {{controlToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "symbol": "BTCUSDT",
  "timeframe": "M5",
  "candleLimit": 18000
}

### Reconcile Bybit open orders, positions, and executions
POST {{baseUrl}}/execution/reconcile
Authorization: Bearer {{controlToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "symbol": "BTCUSDT"
}

### Cancel an open order by local client order id
POST {{baseUrl}}/execution/orders/cancel
Authorization: Bearer {{controlToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "symbol": "BTCUSDT",
  "clientOrderId": "bt-BTCUSDT-1719705600000-1-B"
}
